Bertelsmann’s Prinovis Interested in Schlott Unit, HB Reports

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-03-14T07:10:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/bertelsmann-s-prinovis-interested-in-schlott-unit-hb-reports.html
Bertelsmann AG’s printing unit
Prinovis is interested in buying  Schlott Gruppe AG (SHT) ’s Sebald
business, Handelsblatt  reported , citing an unidentified person
familiar with the situation.  Prinovis inspected the Nuremberg, Germany, operations on
Thursday and Friday and is looking at the books, the newspaper
said.  German media group Hubert Burda Media Holding GmbH & Co. is
also interested in the business, Handelsblatt reported, citing
people close to the negotiations. Burda declined to comment, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 